summary: this mod replaces the music of skyrim
descriptionHtml:
This mod is a port of my Xbox mod on bethesda.net  It replaces all Soundtracks of the base game + DLC content of Dawnguard, Hearthfire and Dragonborn with tracks mostly coming from Lord of the rings, Witcher 3 and WoW.

So far i added over 130 Tracks to the game

Here's a small list of some  tracks

Falkreath: Forest of Elwynn (day)
Solitude: The realm of Gondor
Winterhold College: Khadgars theme
Dawnstar: Crows Perch theme
Whiterun: LOTRO Rohan theme, The two towers: Edoras
Windhelm: Sound of laketown
Morthal: Ladies of the Woods
Riften: Whoreson Junior Theme
Inside Castles: Sound of the Alliance (Warcraft Movie)

Various LOTR, Witcher and WoW theme for both exploration and Combat in Skyrim and Solstheim

and many more!
author: Ramsiis
